{#title}
^1 LETTERS
^3 Concerning the
^1 Love of GOD,
^4 Between the Author of the
^3 Proposal to the *Ladies*
^4 *and*
^3 Mr. _JOHN NORRIS:_

Wherein his late Discourse, shewing, That it ought to be intire and exclusive of all other Loves, is further Cleared and Justified.
